Here are some statistics from Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Olga Kharif:

To pass the chartered financial analyst exams and put the =E2=80=9CCFA=E2=
=80=9D letters on your r=C3=A9sum=C3=A9, at least 900 hours of study are re=
commended. Hitting the books for 300 to 400 hours is advised for the certif=
ied public accountant exam, which is usually taken by prospective CPAs who =
have completed an undergraduate degree in the subject.
However, to become a =E2=80=9CCertified Cryptocurrency Expert,=E2=80=9D or =
CCE, all you need is $229 and time for 11 hours of online coursework offere=
d by Blockchain Council. If that=E2=80=99s too much of a time commitment, y=
ou can receive a =E2=80=9CCryptocurrency and Blockchain Certificate=E2=80=
=9D elsewhere by taking just four hours of coursework, passing a 20-questio=
n test and shelling out $795.

Well. Sure. Look, I myself have spent at least 11 hours online learning abo=
