0a82db" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" st=
yle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-widt=
h: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgroun=
d-color: #ccc;">Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Olga Kharif</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To pass the chartered financial analyst exams =
and put the =E2=80=9CCFA=E2=80=9D letters on your r=C3=A9sum=C3=A9, at leas=
t 900 hours of study are recommended. Hitting the books for 300 to 400 hour=
s is advised for the certified public accountant exam, which is usually tak=
en by prospective CPAs who have completed an undergraduate degree in the su=
bject.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">However, to become a =E2=80=9CCertified Crypto=
currency Expert,=E2=80=9D or CCE, all you need is $229 and time for 11 hour=
s of online coursework offered by Blockchain Council. If that=E2=80=99s too=
 much of a time commitment, you can receive a =E2=80=9CCryptocurrency and B=
lockchain Certificate=E2=80=9D elsewhere by taking just four hours of cours=
ework, passing a 20-question test and shelling out $795.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well. Sure. Look, I myself have spent at least=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34726086.260360/a=
HR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9mZWF0dXJlcy8yMDIyLXRoZS1jcnlwdG8tc3Rvcnkv=
P2NtcGlkPUJCRDAzMTgyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1=
uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDMxOCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07c=
eef4b8524a319a23cBe8c245c9" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" =
target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important=
; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-sty=
le: solid; background-color: #ccc;">11 hours online</a> learning about cryp=
to, and I do not want to be <em>too</em> skeptical about crypto education. =
But=C2=A0these numbers strike me as=C2=A0reasonable. Of course the CFA prog=
ram should be harder than the crypto program.=C2=A0One model that you could=
 have for crypto is that it is=C2=A0<em>finance=C2=A0</em>without the=C2=A0=
<em>content</em>.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So: A share of stock is an electronic token th=
at you can buy or sell for money. Sometimes a lot of people want to buy a s=
tock, and its price goes up. Other times, people want to sell it, and its p=
rice goes down. Why do they want to buy or sell it? Various reasons: Perhap=
s they got tax refunds or stimulus checks, perhaps the chief executive offi=
cer of the company that issued the stock did something interesting=C2=A0or =
got arrested, perhaps the company announced good earnings or bad earnings o=
r a new product or a computer hack. But the=C2=A0<em>traditional=C2=A0</em>=
reason is that a share of stock represents a partial ownership interest in =
a company, and the long-term value of the stock is the present value of its=
 future cash flows. You can estimate that value by projecting=C2=A0those fu=
ture cash flows and performing math to compute their present value. Differe=
nt people will have different estimates, so there will be trades, and those=
 estimates will change over time =E2=80=94=C2=A0with the company=E2=80=99s =
prospects, with discount rates, with macroeconomic conditions =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0so there will be volatility. And if you want to make money trading stock=
s, traditionally, you go and learn about companies and products and busines=
s models and accounting and discounted cash flow modeling and all the other=
 things that go into estimating the values of stocks, either because you wa=
nt to get good at estimating values or because you want to know what=C2=A0<=
em>other=C2=A0</em>people, the ones you are trading against, are up to.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A crypto token is also an electronic token tha=
t you can buy or sell for money, but in a purified form. There=E2=80=99s no=
 company, no product, no earnings, no cash flow. Sometimes a lot of people =
want to buy the token, and its price goes up; other times, they want to sel=
l, and its price goes down. You have the most salient feature of finance =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0a volatile=C2=A0electronic token that you can trade =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0without any of the other features. There is less to learn!</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh this is unfair and oversimplified,=C2=A0<em=
>your=C2=A0</em>crypto project is different,=C2=A0<em>your=C2=A0</em>crypto=
 project is empowering communities with real products and not just an empty=
 vessel for financial speculation. But Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Muyao Shen <a hr=
ef=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34726086.260360/aHR0cHM=
6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDMtMTMvbWVtZWNvaW4tdH=
JhZGluZy12b2x1bWUtcmlzZXMtdG8tbGV2ZWxzLWxhc3Qtc2Vlbi1iZWZvcmUtY3J5cHRvLWJ1Y=
mJsZS1idXJzdD9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMzE4MjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0=
bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDAzMTgmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R=
1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd3bb821c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D=
"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: non=
e !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; borde=
r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">reported last week</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The memecoin frenzy in the digital-asset marke=
t shows no signs of stopping, with trading volumes now at levels last seen =
just before the burst of the last crypto bubble more than two years ago.</p=
>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Considered as some of the most speculative and=
 volatile cryptocurrencies, memecoins such as Dogwifhat and Pepe are far ou=
tstripping the gains registered by market bellwether Bitcoin that has domin=
ated the headlines. Trading volume for the top memecoins, which often trade=
 for a fraction of a cent, reached nearly $80 billion in the past week, acc=
ording to data compiled by blockchain data firm Kaiko. That=E2=80=99s the h=
ighest since October 2021. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Memecoins have been a long-existing phenomenon=
 in crypto, as small investors and promoters see the microscopic prices of =
memecoins as an opportunity to quick post huge returns despite the lack of =
traditional fundamentals. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A group of dogwifhat token holders announced l=
ast week a public fundraising campaign to put the dogwifhat meme on the Las=
 Vegas Sphere. The group has already reached its target goal of $650,000 in=
 the USDC stablecoin, based on the transaction history of the digital walle=
t for the fundraise. But it=E2=80=99s unclear whether and when the fund wil=
l be used to promote the meme in Las Vegas.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What are dogwifhat=E2=80=99s fundamentals? Wel=
l:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Its logo is a dog, with a hat.</li>=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If people kick in enough money, maybe =
they can put a picture of the dog with the hat on the Las Vegas Sphere, whi=
ch might encourage more people to kick in more money.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What does the multiple-choice exam question ab=
out this look like?=C2=A0Or <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/34726086.260360/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhlYmxvY2suY28vcG9zdC8yODMwMjUvc=
29sYW5hLW1lbWVjb2luLXNsZXJmLWJ1cm4/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB240a68cf" itemp=
rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;">today</a> we got=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/34726086.260360/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhlYmxvY2suY28vcG9zdC8yODMwMjUvc29s=
YW5hLW1lbWVjb2luLXNsZXJmLWJ1cm4/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC240a68cf" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
the story of Slerf</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A new Solana-based memecoin, Slerf, has faced =
significant challenges after the project=E2=80=99s developer accidentally b=
urnt a major portion of the token supply =E2=80=94 effectively losing $10 m=
illion, or the entirety, of presale participants=E2=80=99 money.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"Guys I f=E2=80=94ed up," the project's offici=
al X account wrote. "I burned the LP and the tokens that were set aside for=
 the airdrop. Mint authority is already revoked so I can not mint them. The=
re is nothing I can do to fix this. I am so f=E2=80=94ing sorry."</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Slerf team later went to an X Spaces to el=
aborate further on the situation. "I'm sick to my stomach," team member Slo=
rg said in a Space on X. "I'm literally about to throw up."</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"I'm lost for words," they added. "I don't kno=
w what to do."</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Poor Slorg. Basically the way crypto works is =
that a guy named Slorg <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
