ecutive officer=C2=A0and then <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusines=
s.com/click/34726086.260360/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2F=
ydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDEtMTYvbW9yZ2FuLXN0YW5sZXktbGVha2VkLXNvbWUtYmxvY2stdHJhZG=
