<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are an investment adviser, and you tell=
 prospective clients =E2=80=9CI will think very hard about what the best in=
vestments are for you, and then buy the ones that I think will go up and av=
oid the ones that I think will go down,=E2=80=9D and in fact you pick a bun=
ch of stocks at random in five minutes and spend the rest of your time watc=
hing TikTok videos, will you get in trouble? Man, I don=E2=80=99t know, may=
be. Probably. But it is hard to <em>prove=C2=A0</em>that you=C2=A0<em>didn=
=E2=80=99t=C2=A0</em>think seriously about your clients=E2=80=99 investment=
s. Nobody witnesses your thinking, or lack thereof; that is internal to you=
.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand, if you say =E2=80=9CI have =
