for comment.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">SEC Chair Gary Gensler has been warning firms =
about over-hyped statements related to AI. The agency has specific authorit=
ies to oversee statements that money managers make to investors. In Februar=
y, Gensler also warned publicly traded companies to avoid =E2=80=9CAI washi=
ng=E2=80=9D when talking to investors about their use of the technology.</p=
