</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Delphia was=C2=A0<em>not=C2=A0</em>in fact usi=
ng client=E2=80=99s social media and banking data to make investment decisi=
ons, but what if it did? How would that be predictive? I could imagine that=
