e it to make some predictions: Robinhood has a lot of customers, and its in=
terface magnifies trends; knowing that a bunch of Robinhood customers are b=
uying Stock X =E2=80=94=C2=A0or posting about it on social media for that m=
atter =E2=80=94=C2=A0might help you predict that Stock X was going up. But =
Delphia =E2=80=9Cmanaged approximately $7 million for about 29,000 individu=
al retail accounts through robo-advisory services=C2=A0and approximately $1=
80 million for five pooled investment vehicles.=E2=80=9D How much predictiv=
e power would you get from their social media posts?=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile, =E2=80=9CGlobal Predictions represe=
